║           LLM Inference Node — Debian Live                   ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                                              ║
║  This machine is running as a distributed LLM inference      ║
║  node. On first boot, it will:                               ║
║                                                              ║
║   1. Build the NVIDIA GPU driver (takes ~3 min)              ║
║   2. Start Ollama on port 11434 (all interfaces)             ║
║   3. Start the exo distributed inference daemon              ║
║   4. Pull a starter model (qwen2.5-coder:7b)                 ║
║                                                              ║
║  Run  node-status  to see GPU, Ollama, and network info.     ║
║  Logs: journalctl -u llm-node-setup -f                       ║
║                                                              ║
║  SSH password (root): llmnode                                ║
║  Change it:  passwd root                                      ║
